rows.label: qst201414_msg0001
rows.name: Ah, we're kinda in a bind here.

rows.label: qst201414_msg0002
rows.name: Yeah. No kidding...

rows.label: qst201414_msg0003
rows.name:
Every bout so far has ended in a draw.
Who'd have thought it?

rows.label: qst201414_msg0004
rows.name:
At this rate, the sun'll be up before we
know who's got the most Girl Power.

rows.label: qst201414_msg0005
rows.name:
I'm sure the next person who comes
by will be able to help us...

rows.label: qst201414_msg0006
rows.name:
Let's agree to just go with whatever
they say...

rows.label: qst201414_msg0007
rows.name: Got it!

rows.label: qst201414_msg0008
rows.name: Nia!

rows.label: qst201414_msg0009
rows.name: Good timing, girl!

rows.label: qst201414_msg0010
rows.name:
Huh? What is it...? I dunno if I'm up for
any more of your weird games...

rows.label: qst201414_msg0011
rows.name: No, it's nothing strange!

rows.label: qst201414_msg0012
rows.name:
We just want you to tell us who has
the most Girl Power. Me, or Zakuro?

rows.label: qst201414_msg0013
rows.name: Girl...Power...?

rows.label: qst201414_msg0014
rows.name:
Huh? You still aren't done with your
stupid contest yet?

rows.label: qst201414_msg0015
rows.name:
Hey, come on. Just give us an answer.
Don't hold back! Just serve it as it
comes!

rows.label: qst201414_msg0016
rows.name: Out with it, Nia!

rows.label: qst201414_msg0017
rows.name:
It's me, right? I've got the most
Girl Power.

rows.label: qst201414_msg0018
rows.name:
No way! I've got more Girl Power in
my little finger!

rows.label: qst201414_msg0019
rows.name:
You need to back that up with
something, Hikari! All your Girl
Power's in your mouth!

rows.label: qst201414_msg0020
rows.name: That's what you think, right, Nia?

rows.label: qst201414_msg0021
rows.name:
NO! That's not what you think at all,
is it, Nia?

rows.label: qst201414_msg0023
rows.name: Okay. I decided...

rows.label: qst201414_msg0024
rows.name: Who is it?

rows.label: qst201414_msg0025
rows.name: Gulp...!

rows.label: qst201414_msg0026
rows.name:
I decided...not to take part in this
bloody farce!

rows.label: qst201414_msg0027
rows.name: Nia!

rows.label: qst201414_msg0028
rows.name: Wait!
